<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
  <p>Hello <%= @reservation.driver.first_name %>,</p>
    <p>
    Our records indicate that you had a reservation for today at <%= @start_time.partition(' ').last %> going to <%= @reservation.site.title %>
    and haven't yet completed a Vehicle Report. If you didn't use the vehicle please let us know so that the reservation can be canceled. 
    If you did use the vehicle, please go <%= link_to "HERE", reservation_url(@reservation) %> to fill out the Vehicle Report now.
    </p>
    <p>
    Thank you,<br>
    Your <%= @reservation.program.unit.name %> RideShare Team
    </p>
    <p>
      You can email <%= @unit_email %> or call the office at: <%= @contact_phone %>.
    </p>
    <p>
      To view/modify/cancel reservations, click here
      <%= link_to "LSA RideShare", welcome_pages_student_url %>
    </p>
    <%= render 'garage_service' %> 
    <p>
    That was an automated email.
    You received it because you are a driver in the LSA RideShare application.
    You can unsubscribe from automated notifications <%= link_to "HERE", mailer_subscriptions_url %>.
  </p>
  </body>
</html>
